# HEYDAY project context

**READ FIRST** — Skim this file + `heyday-workflow.mdc` before coding. User requirements are acceptance criteria, not nice-to-haves. Mockups/screenshots are acceptance tests. Trust ROUTES, API, and DOMAIN sections here over stale README changelogs.

**GOAL** — Real estate operations platform (Express/SQLite API + React/Vite SPA). Path: `/Users/rexramza/Desktop/heyday`.

## STACK

- Root `npm run dev` → nodemon API `:3001` + Vite `:5173` (proxy `/api`)
- Server: Node ESM, Express, better-sqlite3, JWT cookie auth, `foreign_keys ON`
- Client: React 18, React Router, Tailwind
- Build: `npm run build` (client only). **No commits unless user asks.**

## DEPLOY

- Repo: `github.com/R3xRamza/heyday`
- Production: `https://hub.theheydaygroup.com` (Railway)
- `railway.toml`: install + build client + `npm start` (serves `client/dist`)
