## LAYOUT & DESIGN

- `DashboardLayout` = Sidebar + TopNav + main; `marginLeft` from `sidebarWidth`
- Brand: feather (#134041), sky, lemon; Tailwind tokens `primary-container`, `secondary`, `surface-*`
- `html` font-size 18px. Icons: `shared/Icon.jsx` + lucide in Sidebar
- Full-bleed pages: **no `max-w` caps** that leave dead right margin on main content — use `w-full` + horizontal padding only (CRM Hub / Vendors already follow this; prefer for other list hubs going forward)
- Reuse `DateText`, `TeamAvatar`, `DashboardLayout`

## DOMAIN — Transactions

- Representing: seller, buyer, landlord, tenant (legacy `seller_and_buyer` normalized)
- Parties: Traditional = Agent, Title, Cooperating Agent, Client, Lender (+ custom); Rent/lease = Agent, Client (+ custom). Active requires Agent+Client; Traditional pending also requires Title, Cooperating Agent, Lender. `workflow_status`: setup via `TransactionSetup` until active
- Key dates: `listing_date`, `important_date` (expiration), `close_date`, `acceptance_date`, `option_end_date`
- **List filters** (`TransactionsList.jsx`): Active Transactions, Coming Soon, Current Listings, Pending, Closed, All
- **Current Listings columns:** Address, Type, Price, Listing Date, **Expiration** (`important_date`) — no Agent column
- **Listings KPI card** subtitle: **Active**
- **Create (step 1):** address/city/state/zip + required Agent (no default) — `validateCreateTransaction`; client name in setup later
- **Delete:** detach `transaction_activity.task_id` → delete tasks → delete transaction (FK-safe)
- **Checklist view** (`TransactionWorkspace.jsx`): scrollable panel ~32rem min height; task rows `font-medium`; complete = strikethrough only (no COMPLETED label); click row → detail sidebar
- List view state: `transactions-list-view-v1` sessionStorage; `TransactionsNavTracker`

## DOMAIN — Tasks

- Status: pending | complete; optional `transaction_id`, `due_date`, template link
- **TeamTaskOverview** `/tasks` — workload cards, milestones
- **UserTaskDashboard** `/tasks/:userId` — filters, table/calendar; categories: transaction + admin
- **TaskHubTabs** + **TaskHubPersonHeader** on person dashboards
- Calendar display: `displayTaskTitle()` → nickname || title

## DOMAIN — Project Dashboard

- `/tasks/:userId/projects` — projects-only card grid (optional target date / `deadline`); no personal todo columns
- Write: owner or admin. Components: `client/src/components/projects/*`
- Day-to-day tasks live under Admin Tasks; projects track longer initiatives

## DOMAIN — CRM

- Contacts with birthday, anniversary, partner fields. Gmail sync → `contact_activity`
- Hub: `/crm` Contacts + `/crm/vendors` Vendors via in-hub tabs (`CrmHubTabs`) — **no** separate sidebar Vendors item
- Detail: `/crm/:id`
- Vendors: standalone `vendors` table (name, company, free-text category, phone, email, website, notes); team **likes** via `vendor_likes` (multiple likes + optional notes per person); any auth user CRUD via `/api/vendors` (+ `POST /:id/likes`, `DELETE /:id/likes/:likeId`); seeded from bundled `server/data/vendors-seed.json` + CRM stage Vendors links; no transaction FKs yet
- Full-width CRM content (no content `max-w` caps)

## DOMAIN — Checklists

- `/checklists` — `ChecklistEditor.jsx`: multi-line title, calendar nickname, default assignee, timing
- `template_tasks`: `default_role`, `calendar_nickname`, timing_* → applied via `applyChecklists.js`
- Multiple checklists per transaction (`transaction_checklists` junction)

## DOMAIN — Marketing Calendar

